What is this?














	Herbalife is a global nutrition company that has helped people pursue an active, healthy life since 1980. Our products, which include protein shakes and snacks, energy and fitness drinks, vitamins and nutritional supplements, and a complete bath and body care line, are available exclusively through Herbalife Distributors in over 90 countries.


		Net sales of $4.5 billion in 2016

		We believe the quality of our products and the effectiveness of our distribution network, coupled with geographic expansion, have been the primary reasons for our success throughout our 37 year history.

		We pursue profitability and growth to increase shareholder value.


 Herbalife Investor Presentation May 2017


